# Otzar Ha'Sofer — cloud configuration (optional).
#
# Leave these unset and the app runs fully local, exactly as before —
# no accounts, all data in the browser's IndexedDB.
#
# To enable the Scribes' Cloud (accounts + private cross-device sync),
# create a Supabase project (see DEPLOY.md), then set:
#
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key
#
# The anon key is public by design — it is shipped to every browser, and
# security is enforced by the database's row-level-security policies
# (see supabase/schema.sql), not by keeping this key secret.
